<!-- HERO -->
<section class="bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(15,23,42,.9),rgba(30,41,59,.85)),url(&#39;https://legalx24.com/img/incorporation-hero.jpg&#39;)]  bg-cover bg-center text-white text-center px-5 py-[110px]"> 
      <h1 class="font-black text-[clamp(34px,4vw,48px)] mb-2"> Company Incorporation &amp; Business Registration </h1> 
      <p class="max-w-[900px] mx-auto text-[17px] leading-[1.8]"> Company incorporation is the legal process of forming a registered business entity. Proper incorporation ensures legal recognition, compliance, and protection of business interests. </p> </section> 
   <section class="py-[55px] px-5 container mx-auto"> 
      <div class="row items-center">
         <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h2 class="font-extrabold text-[clamp(24px,3vw,32px)] text-[#0f172a] mb-3 after:content-[&#39;&#39;] after:block after:w-[60px] after:h-[3px] after:bg-emerald-500 after:mt-1"> What is Company Incorporation? </h2>
            <p class="text-[15.8px] leading-[1.85] text-[#334155] mb-2"> Incorporation is the process of registering a business under applicable corporate laws to obtain separate legal identity. Once incorporated, the company becomes distinct from its owners. </p>
            <p class="text-[15.8px] leading-[1.85] text-[#334155]"> Incorporation provides limited liability protection, credibility, structured governance, and ease of fundraising. </p>
         </div>
         <div class="col-lg-6"> 
            <img src="https://legalx24.com/img/incorporation-1.jpg" class="w-full rounded-[12px] shadow-[0_18px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,.2)] transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-[5px] hover:shadow-[0_28px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,.3)]" alt="Company Incorporation Meeting" data-themekey="#"/> &#160;</div>
      </div> </section> 
   <section class="py-[55px] px-5 bg-[#f8fafc] container mx-auto"> 
      <h2 class="font-extrabold text-[clamp(24px,3vw,32px)] text-[#0f172a] mb-3 after:content-[&#39;&#39;] after:block after:w-[60px] after:h-[3px] after:bg-emerald-500 after:mt-1"> Types of Business Entities </h2> 
      <p class="text-[15.8px] leading-[1.85] text-[#334155] mb-2"> Businesses may be incorporated as Private Limited Companies, Limited Liability Partnerships (LLP), One Person Companies (OPC), or Public Limited Companies depending upon operational requirements. </p> 
      <p class="text-[15.8px] leading-[1.85] text-[#334155]"> Each structure offers different compliance requirements, taxation implications, and liability protection. </p> 
      <div class="bg-white border-l-[6px] border-emerald-500 p-[22px] rounded-[10px] my-[25px] shadow-[0_12px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,.08)] font-semibold"> Choosing the right entity structure is critical for long-term growth, funding opportunities, and regulatory compliance. </div> </section> 
   <section class="py-[55px] px-5 container mx-auto"> 
      <div class="row items-center">
         <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2">
            <h2 class="font-extrabold text-[clamp(24px,3vw,32px)] text-[#0f172a] mb-3 after:content-[&#39;&#39;] after:block after:w-[60px] after:h-[3px] after:bg-emerald-500 after:mt-1"> Incorporation Process </h2>
            <p class="text-[15.8px] leading-[1.85] text-[#334155] mb-2"> The incorporation process involves name reservation, drafting of constitutional documents, filing registration forms, and obtaining statutory approvals. </p>
            <p class="text-[15.8px] leading-[1.85] text-[#334155]"> Upon approval, a Certificate of Incorporation is issued, granting legal status to the entity. </p>
         </div>
         <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1"> 
            <img src="https://legalx24.com/img/incorporation-2.jpg" class="w-full rounded-[12px] shadow-[0_18px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,.2)] transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-[5px] hover:shadow-[0_28px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,.3)]" alt="Startup Registration Consultation" data-themekey="#"/> &#160;</div>
      </div> </section> 
   <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0f172a] to-[#1e293b] text-white py-[55px] px-5"> 
      <div class="container mx-auto">
         <h2 class="font-extrabold text-[clamp(24px,3vw,32px)] mb-3"> Compliance &amp; Post-Incorporation Requirements </h2>
         <p class="text-[15.8px] leading-[1.85] mb-2"> Incorporated entities must comply with statutory filings, board meetings, annual returns, tax registrations, and regulatory reporting obligations. </p>
         <p class="text-[15.8px] leading-[1.85]"> Non-compliance may result in penalties or legal complications. </p>
      </div> </section> 
   <section class="py-[55px] px-5 container mx-auto"> 
      <h2 class="font-extrabold text-[clamp(24px,3vw,32px)] text-[#0f172a] mb-3 after:content-[&#39;&#39;] after:block after:w-[60px] after:h-[3px] after:bg-emerald-500 after:mt-1"> Importance of Professional Guidance </h2> 
      <p class="text-[15.8px] leading-[1.85] text-[#334155] mb-2"> Proper drafting of Memorandum &amp; Articles, compliance planning, and structuring advice ensure smooth operations and risk mitigation. </p> 
      <p class="text-[15.8px] leading-[1.85] text-[#334155]"> Legalx24 assists startups, entrepreneurs, and corporations in seamless business incorporation and compliance management. </p> </section> 
   <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#047857] to-[#065f46] text-white text-center py-[65px] px-5"> 
      <h2 class="text-[28px] font-black"> Start Your Business with Legal Compliance </h2> 
      <p class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto mt-2 mb-6"> Get expert legal support for company incorporation, regulatory approvals, and structured business setup. </p> 
      <a class="inline-block bg-emerald-500 hover:bg-emerald-600 px-[40px] py-[12px] rounded-[35px] font-bold transition"> Incorporate Your Company </a> </section> 
